About Expense Tracker

Expense Tracker is a monthly expense tracking application built with React. It helps you keep track of your income and expenses, providing valuable insights into your spending habits.

With Expense Tracker, you can easily add your expenses, categorize them, and view a summary of your monthly spending. The application also provides visual representations of your expenses, such as charts and graphs, to help you analyze your financial situation.

Start managing your finances today with Expense Tracker and gain control over your expenses!
